SOCIAL AND BUSINESS IMPACT

Insurance fraud not only affects insurance companies but also impacts society and honest policyholders.
Implementing a machine learning-based fraud detection system can bring several positive social and business benefits.

1️.REDUCTION IN FINANCIAL LOSSES

Fraudulent insurance claims lead to huge financial losses for insurance companies every year.
A machine learning-based fraud detection system can identify suspicious claims early and help companies reduce financial losses significantly.

2️. LOWER INSURANCE PREMIUMS FOR CUSTOMERS

When fraud increases, insurance companies often raise premiums for all customers to recover losses.
By detecting and preventing fraud, companies can maintain fair pricing and reduce unnecessary premium increases for honest customers.

3️. FASTER CLAIM PROCESSING

With automated fraud detection, genuine claims can be processed faster because the system quickly
identifies which claims are legitimate. This improves customer satisfaction and service quality.

4️. IMPROVED OPERATIONAL EFFICIENCY

Manual fraud investigation requires significant time and resources. A machine learning model helps automate the detection process,
allowing investigators to focus only on high-risk claims, thereby improving operational efficiency.

5️.DATA-DRIVEN DECISION MAKING

The fraud detection system provides insights into patterns and trends in fraudulent activities. 
This helps insurance companies make better strategic decisions based on data analysis.

6️. ENHANCED TRUST IN INSURANCE SYSTEMS

Fraudulent activities reduce trust in insurance systems. Detecting and preventing fraud helps
maintain transparencyand trust between insurance providers and customers.

7️. SUPPORT FOR INVESTIGATIVE TEAMS

The system acts as a decision-support tool for fraud investigators by flagging suspicious claims,
making it easier to prioritize investigations and allocate resources effectively.

8️. SCALABILITY FOR LARGE DATA

Insurance companies handle large volumes of claim data daily. A machine learning-based system can 
analyze large datasets efficiently,making it suitable for large-scale operations.
